"How do I bind an NFC tag to a plant?" = "如何将 NFC 标签绑定到植物？";
"Tap + on the home screen, then scan your NFC tag on the NFC scan page before creating your plant." = "在首页点击 +，然后在 NFC 扫描页面扫描标签，再创建植物。";
"What NFC tags are supported?" = "支持哪些 NFC 标签？";
"Any NDEF-compatible NFC tag (e.g. NTAG215, NTAG213). Tap the + button and scan your tag first." = "任何兼容 NDEF 的 NFC 标签（如 NTAG215、NTAG213）均可使用，请先点击 + 扫描标签。";
"How do reminders work?" = "提醒如何工作？";
